title: 1909/289 Grey Street, South Bank, Qld 4101
agency_address: Shop 2, 128 Merivale Street, SOUTH BRISBANE, QLD 4101
description:
OPEN HOME DIRECTIONS - 
Please enter via  the Southpoint Entrance on Grey Street, next to 'The Melanoma Centre'.

TO BE SOLD ON OR BEFORE AUCTION. GOING... GOING... GONE.

Opportunities of this calibre are exceptionally rare. With uninterrupted city and river views that will never be built out, this residence secures a lifestyle that is truly without equal.

Southpoint stands as one of Brisbane's most prestigious addresses, offering world-class, six-star resident facilities. Within 196 apartments over twenty-one levels, only twenty-four three-bedroom residences were ever released from Levels 16 to 21 on the city-facing side, making this a tightly held and highly coveted opportunity.

Properties of this nature are seldom available, and discerning buyers are urged to act swiftly to secure what is unquestionably one of South Bank's most exclusive offerings.

Welcome to Southpoint, an exceptional residence that combines luxury, comfort, and convenience. This stunning high-rise building is located in the heart of South Bank, one of Brisbane's most vibrant and sought-after locations. There is no other suburb in Brisbane that compares.

As you enter this spectacular apartment, you will be greeted by a spacious and open living area that is flooded with natural light. The large open plan living and dining area opens out to the expansive balcony, with large sliding floor to ceiling glass doors, to enjoy the magnificent view from anywhere.

The exceptional kitchen boasts stainless steel Miele appliances; built-in fridge and freezer, large 5 burner gas cooktop and rangehood, two wall ovens, integrated microwave, dishwasher, plus stone benchtops and a large island bench. Capture the spectacular views off the mirrored splashback. Handy home office area just through the hallway.

The built-in bar, incorporating multiple temperate control wine fridges with overhead display cabinetry is truly a work of art, combining style and functionality in a way that is both impressive and practical. It is the perfect addition to any home that values luxury and sophistication. Every aspect of apartment living has been thoughtfully incorporated and implemented to add to the ease of apartment living.

Journey through into the master wing, where you are greeted with a supersized walk-through robe featuring luxury makeup vanity station, expansive ensuite and direct access to the balcony with jaw dropping views from the master boudoir.

The second bedroom offers a large walk-through robe as well as direct balcony access. The third bedroom provides built-ins and room for a desk or charging station. There is a separate, conveniently located powder room, plus a good-sized main bathroom, as well as a full-sized separate laundry.

Looking for your perfect Brisbane Bolt Hold in the ultimate lifestyle destination then this is the perfect lockup and leave. Offering exceptional versatility, this luxury apartment is perfectly suited to families, couples, and professionals alike, with its premium design and prime Brisbane location.

Features:
- Perfect North-East facing aspect.
- Separate ducted and zoned air conditioning.
- Clipsal C-BUS DLT One-Touch Light Control.
- Integrated DLS in-wall and in-ceiling home audio system.
- Plush carpets, superior finishes and fixtures.
- Beautiful wood finished floors through living areas.
- High security building.
- Located in the Brisbane State High Catchment.
- Private Schools within walking distance.
- Public transport, bus, rail and city cat.
- Mater Hospital within walking distance.

The rooftop pool and amenities at Southpoint Building are truly a sight to behold, after a workout or a swim, head over to the rooftop lounge, where you can relax and unwind in style.

Step onto the rooftop and immerse yourself in a world of relaxation and leisure. The rooftop pool is the ultimate retreat, offering a stunning panoramic view of the city skyline and the Brisbane River. Take a dip in the crystal-clear water and soak up the sun on one of the comfortable lounge chairs, while enjoying the warm and inviting ambiance of this luxurious setting.

Rooftop facilities also include a media room, function room, barbeque area and private dining area. The media room will feature a large screen, state-of-the-art sound, and comfortable seating, making it the perfect place to relax and enjoy your favourite movies or TV shows. The function room offers a large open space with plenty of natural light, perfect for hosting meetings or a get together. The private dining area is an elegant, intimate space, designed to provide a fine dining experience for special occasions.

Level 5 houses the 6-star gym, sauna, and steam room and is the perfect way to stay fit and healthy, while also indulging in a little luxury. Come experience it for yourself and see why Southpoint is the ultimate destination for modern inner-city living.

Lastly step out onto the Level 5 BBQ area and prepare to be impressed. This beautifully designed outdoor space features a range of high-end amenities, including multiple BBQ stations, comfortable seating, and stunning city views.

South Bank Brisbane 4101 is a vibrant neighbourhood located on the southern bank of the Brisbane River in Queensland, Australia. It is known for its stunning riverfront parklands, cultural attractions, and world-class dining and entertainment options.

The Parklands, a sprawling 17-hectare park featuring lush gardens, walking and cycling paths, and scenic riverfront views. The Parklands are also home to a range of cultural institutions, including the Queensland Art Gallery, the Queensland Museum, and the State Library of Queensland.


Disclaimer, due to REIQ legislation a price guide isn't available. The website possibly filtered this property into a price range for functionality purposes. Any estimates are not provided by the agent and should not be taken as a price guide.
